 ui-sref=\"speakers\" class=\"btn\">Speaker Details</a></p></div><div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6\"><h3 id=\"perform\">Perform</h3>\n<p>You dont have to be great, just enthusiastic. Try to keep it to \naround six minutes.</p>\n<p><a ui-sref=\"performers\" class=\"btn\">Performer Details</a></p></div></div></div></section><section id=\"schedule\"><div class=\"container-fluid\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6\"><h2>Schedule <select ng-options=\"month.day|date:&quot;MMMM d&quot; group by month.date.getFullYear() for month in index.calendar\" ng-model=\"index.day\"></select></h2><ul class=\"schedule\"><li ng-repeat=\"event in index.day.schedule track by $index\"><div ng-repeat=\"(time, item) in event\" class=\"row row-lg-offset--3\"><div class=\"col-xs-12 col-lg-3 end-lg\"><h5>{{time}} <span class=\"hide-lg\"><span ng-show=\"item.type || item.emoji\"> </span><span ng-show=\"item.emoji\">{{item.emoji}} </span><span ng-show=\"item.type\">{{item.type}}</span></span></h5></div><div ng-show=\"item.person || item.people || item.type\" class=\"col-xs-12 col-lg-9\"><h5 ng-show=\"item.person\"><a ng-href=\"https://twitter.com/{{item.person.twitter}}\" class=\"person\">{{item.person.name}}  @{{item.person.twitter}}</a></h5><h5 ng-show=\"item.people\"><span ng-repeat=\"person in item.people\"><span ng-hide=\"$first\" class=\"separator\">&</span><wbr><a ng-href=\"https://twitter.com/{{person.twitter}}\" class=\"person\">{{person.name}}  @{{person.twitter}}</a></span></h5></div><div ng-show=\"item.type\" class=\"hide-md-down col-lg-3 end-lg\"><h5>{{item.type}}</h5></div><div ng-class=\"{ &quot;border-bottom&quot;: !item.description }\" class=\"col-xs-12 col-lg-9\"><h3 ng-show=\"item.title\" marked=\"item.title\"></h3></div><div ng-show=\"item.emoji &amp;&amp; item.description\" class=\"hide-md-down col-lg-3 end-lg\"><h5>{{item.emoji}}</h5></div><div ng-class=\"{ &quot;col-lg-offset-3&quot;: !item.emoji, &quot;border-bottom&quot;: item.description }\" marked=\"item.description\" class=\"col-xs-12 col-lg-9\"></div></div></li></ul></div></div></div></section><section id=\"sponsors\"><div class=\"container-fluid\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6\"><h2>Sponsors</h2><p>This months WaffleJS is sponsored by <span ng-repeat=\"sponsor in index.day.sponsors\"><span ng-show=\"$middle\">, </span><span ng-show=\"$last &amp;&amp; index.day.sponsors.length === 2\"> and </span><span ng-show=\"$last &amp;&amp; index.day.sponsors.length &gt; 2\">, and </span><a href=\"{{url}}\" ng-repeat=\"(name, url) in sponsor\">{{name}}</a></span>.</p><p>Interested in sponsoring a future event?</p><p><a ui-sref=\"sponsorship\" class=\"btn\">Sponsorship Details</a></p></div><div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6\"><div class=\"row around-xs middle-xs\"><span ng-repeat=\"sponsor in index.day.sponsors\"><a href=\"{{url}}\" ng-repeat=\"(name, url) in sponsor\"><img ng-src=\"/images/sponsors/{{name}}.svg\"></a></span></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"transparency\"><div class=\"container-fluid\"><h2>Transparency</h2><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6\"><h3 id=\"finance\">Finance</h3>\n<p>We donate all proceeds every month. Check out our <a href=\"{{index.day.budget}}\">budget\nspreadsheet</a> to learn more.</p>\n</div><div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6\"><h3 id=\"planning\">Planning</h3>\n<p>We plan everything out in the open. Come chat with us on <a href=\"http://slack.borojs.com/\">Slack</a>\nor chime in on <a href=\"https://github.com/wafflejs/wafflejs.github.io/issues\">GitHub</a>.</p>\n</div></div></div></section></div>");}.call(this,"className" in locals_for_with?locals_for_with.className:typeof className!=="undefined"?className:undefined));;return buf.join("");
